# 🎬 Movie Booking System (Python OOP)

A console-based **Movie Booking System** developed using **Python** and **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** concepts. This project allows users to select movies, book tickets, make payments, verify OTPs, and generate booking receipts.

## 🚀 Features

* 🎥 Movie Selection
* 🏢 Theater Selection
* 🎟 Ticket Booking
* 💺 Seat Availability Check
* 💳 Online (UPI) Payment
* 💵 Cash Payment
* 🔐 OTP Generation & Verification
* 🔑 UPI PIN Verification
* 🧾 Booking Receipt Generation
* 📄 Booking History Saved to File
* 🆔 Unique Booking ID Generation
* 🕒 Booking Date & Time
* 🧮 GST Calculation
* 🧱 Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* Python 3.x
* OOP (Classes & Objects)
* File Handling
* Random Module
* UUID Module
* Datetime Module

